          </m:math>
        </equation>
        <para id="id170520">
proving the relationship as desired.</para>
      </section>
      <section id="uid11">
        <title>Time Shift</title>
        <para id="id170535">The operation of convolution has the following property for all continuous time signals <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math> where <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msub><m:mi>S</m:mi><m:mi>T</m:mi></m:msub></m:math> is the time shift operator.</para>
