      <section id="uid13">
        <title>Differentiation</title>
        <para id="id171306">The operation of convolution has the following property for all continuous time signals <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math>.</para>
        <equation id="id171334">
          <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
